OL,6,FWatch the Supreme Court's ruling in
OL,7,Ffull.
OL,9,FThe terms "woman" and "sex" in the
OL,10,FEquality Act refer to a biological
OL,11,Fwoman and biological sex, the Supreme
OL,12,FCourt has ruled.
OL,14,FDelivering the judgement, Judge Lord
OL,15,FHodge said the "central question" is
OL,16,Fhow the words "woman" and "sex" are
OL,17,Fdefined in the 2010 Equality Act.
