OL,6,FHe said: "Do these terms refer to
OL,7,Fbiological woman or biological sex, or
OL,8,Fis a woman to be interpreted as
OL,9,Fextending to a trans woman with a
OL,10,FGender Recognition Certificate (GRC)?
OL,12,F"The unanimous decision of this court
OL,13,Fis that the terms woman and sex in the
OL,14,FEquality Act 2010 refer to a
OL,15,Fbiological woman and biological sex".
OL,17,FIt follows a long-running legal battle
OL,18,Fover the definition of 'woman' in
OL,19,FScottish legislation between the
OL,20,FScottish government and the campaign
OL,21,Fgroup For Women Scotland (FWS).
