OL,6,FThe group initially brought their case
OL,7,Fagainst the Scottish Government after
OL,8,Fjudges in Edinburgh ruled in 2018 that
OL,9,Fministers were right to say that trans
OL,10,Fwomen with a GRC could sit on public
OL,11,Fboards in posts reserved for women.
OL,13,FFWS previously said that not tying the
OL,14,Fdefinition of sex to its "ordinary
OL,15,Fmeaning" could have far-reaching
OL,16,Fconsequences for sex-based rights, as
OL,17,Fwell as "everyday single-sex services"
OL,18,Flike toilets and hospital wards.
