OL,6,FThe judges delivering their ruling
OL,7,Fwere keen to stress that today's
OL,8,Fjudgment does not diminish trans
OL,9,Fwomen's protections against
OL,10,Fdiscrimination.
OL,12,FReading from their judgement, Lord
OL,13,FHodge stressed that a person "treated
OL,14,Fless favourably because of the
OL,15,Fprotected characteristic of gender
OL,16,Freassignment will be able to claim on
OL,17,Fthat basis."
