OL,6,FReacting to the Supreme Court ruling,
OL,7,Fa Government spokesman said: "We have
OL,8,Falways supported the protection of
OL,9,Fsingle-sex spaces based on biological
OL,10,Fsex.
OL,12,F"This ruling brings clarity and
OL,13,Fconfidence, for women and service
OL,14,Fproviders such as hospitals, refuges,
OL,15,Fand sports clubs.
OL,17,F"Single-sex spaces are protected in
OL,18,Flaw and will always be protected by
OL,19,Fthis Government."
