OL,11,FSpeaking today, she lauded the Supreme
OL,12,FCourt's ruling as a "victory," saying:
OL,13,F"This is a victory for all of the
OL,14,Fwomen who faced personal abuse or lost
OL,15,Ftheir jobs for stating the obvious.
OL,17,F"Women are women and men are men: you
OL,18,Fcannot change your biological sex.
