OL,6,F"The stakes are high and the court's
OL,7,Fdecision will have consequences for
OL,8,Feveryday, single-sex services such as
OL,9,Ftoilets and hospital wards.
OL,11,F"It will determine whether a pregnant
OL,12,Fwoman with a GRC is entitled to
OL,13,Fmaternity leave, what it means to be
