OL,6,FDuring the hearing, Ruth Crawford KC,
OL,7,Frepresenting the Scottish Government,
OL,8,Fsaid a GRC affected a "change in legal
OL,9,Fstatus", and that someone with a GRC
OL,10,F"becomes recognised as belonging to,
OL,11,For becoming, the sex of their acquired
OL,12,Fgender".
OL,14,FShe added: "We submit there are only
OL,15,Ftwo sexes or genders, and a person
OL,16,Fwhose sex becomes that of a man or
OL,17,Fwoman in consequence of a GRC belongs
OL,18,Fto that sex, and will have the
OL,19,Fprotection afforded under the Equality
OL,20,FAct".
